content:
Use social customer service to engage your customer on social media.

Effective May 3, 2022, the Social Customer Service Starter Pack is no longer available to customers who haven't previously enabled this feature. Customers who have previously used and configured the SCS Starter Pack can continue to use it. Customers who didn't enable the Starter Pack before this date can only use Social Customer Service if they have a Social Studio account.

Use the social action on the case or lead feed to respond to social posts. Choose a message type when replying, for example, reply with a direct message on Twitter or a public tweet.

A social post is a Salesforce object that represents a post on a social network such as Facebook or Twitter.
AÂ social persona is a Salesforce object that represents a contact's profile on a social network such as Facebook, or Twitter.
title: Engage and Respond with Social Customer Service
